{"tid":1693653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[FCed]Email左英國翻糖比賽要佢地解釋嗰懷疑被兩件作品政治DQ","createTime":"2019-11-04T17:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T04:51:10.000Z","uid":230324,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a753275c7f19e0ea15d1f4e1fdbef6ee5375f408","tid":1693653,"uid":230324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:27:35.000Z","msg":"事源係<br />\n英國舉辦國際翻糖比賽被大陸西篤灰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689184</a><br />\n<br />\n我就Email 左 大會問佢地到底咩事<br />\n點解可以係一個國際比賽打壓言論自由<br />\n而且已經比中共媒體大作新聞<br />\n<br />\n佢地表示嗰兩個有關香港運動嘅作品<br />\n並<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有因政治而被DQ</span>  而且<br />\n兩件作品都<span style=\"color: red;\">有被評審</span><br />\n<br />\n而作品只係被撤出展覽 <br />\n因為佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">不宣傳政治觀點</span><br />\n同埋有投訴先撤走<br />\n<br />\n其中一個作品最後被DQ<br />\n係因為其中既雨傘裝飾係不可食用材料製成 同埋 好似overhand左先被DQ<br />\n聽講都同嗰參賽者私下討論過<br />\n都承諾會紀念在案同下次會小心<br />\n<br />\n大家接唔接受呢個解釋？"},{"pid":"b8f0d2a9361fa585207a8ec5e4ef6e5dfa889dd6","tid":1693653,"uid":24487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:28:48.000Z","msg":"Post埋個email啦"},{"pid":"9a7c1d05dd09880dd7e0ff6d08278006bf875e0f","tid":1693653,"uid":106580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1ca81a297d8006d2aea300dbeb57f4c3cd165e","tid":1693653,"uid":230324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TO4YOxX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTO4YOxX.png&h=3aac8797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zzeRo6g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzzeRo6g.png&h=a71aff40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e28b3193fef19abd0a1d2b78d3ae682415b6b1a","tid":1693653,"uid":230324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi